				\begin{document}$$AVT= \frac{\int T\left(\lambda \right)\,P\left(\lambda \right) \,S\left(\lambda \right)\,d(\lambda )}{\int P\left(\lambda \right)\, S\left(\lambda \right)\, d(\lambda )}.$$\end{document}
